name: Spell On You (1 of 1)
description:
I'll put a spell on you, & you'll be mine💕

Use this spell for any kind of mischief you may.

Use it on the darkest of nights, or at the brightest light of the day.

Whatever you may choose, it's your choice alone.

For no one will know, who truly controls the throne.

 

(Original)

Art by: @SolarKittyn
